      "rationale": "Not assessed at MRL 2. SST k-ω turbulence model selected based on published precedent for rotary blood pump CFD (Fraser et al., 2011; Hariharan et al., 2011). Model form uncertainty not formally quantified."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
